      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/knn/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "想判断一个陌生人属于哪个圈子，看看他身边的朋友就大概知道了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "knn",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/knn/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "机器学习里最直白的分类器，正是用这个朴素的想法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "knn",
      "section_id": "distance",
      "line_id": "dist-1",
      "filename": "distance-dist-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/knn/xiaoxiao/distance-dist-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "我们先把每个已知类别的样本，画在平面上，用颜色区分类别。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "knn",
      "section_id": "distance",
      "line_id": "dist-2",
      "filename": "distance-dist-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/knn/xiaoxiao/distance-dist-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "来了一个待分类的新点，就计算它到每个样本的距离。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "knn",
      "section_id": "distance",
      "line_id": "dist-3",
      "filename": "distance-dist-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/knn/xiaoxiao/distance-dist-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "挑出距离最近的 k 个样本，它们就是这个新点的邻居。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "knn",
      "section_id": "vote",
      "line_id": "vote-1",
      "filename": "vote-vote-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/knn/xiaoxiao/vote-vote-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "接下来让这 k 个邻居投票，各自报出自己的类别。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "knn",
      "section_id": "vote",
      "line_id": "vote-2",
      "filename": "vote-vote-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/knn/xiaoxiao/vote-vote-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.54,
      "size": 24624,
      "text": "哪个类别的票数最多，新点就归到哪一类。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "knn",
      "section_id": "vote",
      "line_id": "vote-3",
      "filename": "vote-vote-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/knn/xiaoxiao/vote-vote-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "整个过程不需要训练，只要记住全部样本，所以叫惰性学习。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "knn",
      "section_id": "boundary",
      "line_id": "bnd-1",
      "filename": "boundary-bnd-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/knn/xiaoxiao/boundary-bnd-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "把平面上每一点都分类一遍，颜色的交界就是决策边界。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "knn",
      "section_id": "boundary",
      "line_id": "bnd-2",
